			explicabo.
		</p>
		<p>
			<em>[PLACEHOLDER — fill with: founding-team narrative, GLP design, partnership arithmetic, the Arbitrum migration, your personal arc through the rebrand. 400–600 words ideal.]</em>
		</p>
	</Window>

	<Window id="effie" title="Effie Perine LTD. · Operations & Client Relations" initialX={260} initialY={180}>
		<p><b>Effie Perine LTD.</b> — <em>Operations &amp; Client Relations, 2019 – 2020</em></p>
		<p>
			Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Sed do eiusmod
